{
  "metadata": {
    "synopsis": "Avatar Gale has a moment of reflection by himself in a room in the elfsong tavern, shortly after the battle for Baldur's Gate and defeat of the Netherbrain. This dialogue serves to offer the chance to decide the crown's fate for players who didn't get the chance to do this in combat over. It reuses a lot of lines from that dialogue VO-wise, but cinematically feel free to adjust the shots/poses as needed."
  },
  "dialogue": {
    "4": {
      "id": "4",
      "speaker": "Narrator",
      "text": "*The Netherbrain is defeated, Faer\u00fbn is saved, but where you should feel peace you feel only the orb. Restless. Hungry. Yearning.*",
      "context": "CinematicNodeContext: Gale stands at a window, looking out over the Chionthar. If possible, a shot of the Chionthar.",
      "checkflags": [
        "ORI_Gale_Knows_ReadKarsusNotes"
      ],
      "setflags": [],
      "ruletags": [],
      "approval": [],
      "rolls": "",
      "goto": "",
      "link": "36",
      "is_end": false,
      "node_type": "normal",
      "children": {
        "39": {
          "id": "39",
          "speaker": "Narrator",
          "text": "*The Crown is in the depths of the Chionthar. If you salvage the stones, you could claim it, reforge it, and revive the power of Netheril anew.*",
          "context": "InternalNodeContext: KNOWS ABOUT REFORGING CROWN\rNodeContext: Speaking of Gale, who knows that he could reforge the Crown of Karsus - the very thing that allowed the Netherbrain to be dominated and become the Netherbrain",
          "checkflags": [],
          "setflags": [],
          "ruletags": [],
          "approval": [],
          "rolls": "",
          "goto": "",
          "link": "36",
          "is_end": false,
          "node_type": "normal",
          "children": {
            "16": {
              "id": "16",
              "speaker": "Narrator",
              "text": "*Mystra's summons still stands. Bring the Crown to her and she may yet offer you a cure, but there is no guarantee that she will be in a forgiving mood.*",
              "context": "InternalNodeContext: Knows Mystra wants to speak to you\rNodeContext: Gale weighing internally pros and cons of doing what Mystra says",
              "checkflags": [
                "ORI_Gale_State_Met_ElminsterInWYR"
              ],
              "setflags": [],
              "ruletags": [],
              "approval": [],
              "rolls": "",
              "goto": "",
              "link": "36",
              "is_end": false,
              "node_type": "normal",
              "children": {}
            },
            "6": {
              "id": "6",
              "speaker": "Narrator",
              "text": "*You could take the Crown to Mystra, perhaps leverage it for a cure. But there is no guarantee that she will be in a forgiving mood.*",
              "context": "NodeContext: Gale weighing internally pros and cons of interacting with Mystra at this critical juncture",
              "checkflags": [],
              "setflags": [],
              "ruletags": [],
              "approval": [],
              "rolls": "",
              "goto": "",
              "link": "14",
              "is_end": false,
              "node_type": "normal",
              "children": {
                "36": {
                  "id": "36",
                  "speaker": "Narrator",
                  "text": "*Already you feel the orb straining against the confines of Elminster's spell. It will not hold forever. How will you spend the time that you have left?*",
                  "context": "",
                  "checkflags": [],
                  "setflags": [],
                  "ruletags": [],
                  "approval": [],
                  "rolls": "",
                  "goto": "",
                  "link": "14",
                  "is_end": false,
                  "node_type": "normal",
                  "children": {
                    "49": {
                      "id": "49",
                      "speaker": "Player",
                      "text": "It's time the Crown had a new owner - you. The wizard that defeated the Netherbrain.",
                      "context": "",
                      "checkflags": [
                        "ORI_Gale_Knows_ReadKarsusNotes"
                      ],
                      "setflags": [
                        "ORI_Gale_State_ClaimedCrown"
                      ],
                      "ruletags": [],
                      "approval": [],
                      "rolls": "",
                      "goto": "",
                      "link": "14",
                      "is_end": false,
                      "node_type": "normal",
                      "children": {
                        "12": {
                          "id": "12",
                          "speaker": "Narrator",
                          "text": "*The very air around you thrums with anticipation, and fear. Can you really handle such power, such authority?*",
                          "context": "CinematicNodeContext: Gale contemplating his newfound power, feeling his isolation from his surroundings and his party\rNodeContext: speaking of Gale, who is fairly sure he's about to become a god",
                          "checkflags": [],
                          "setflags": [],
                          "ruletags": [],
                          "approval": [],
                          "rolls": "",
                          "goto": "",
                          "link": "14",
                          "is_end": false,
                          "node_type": "normal",
                          "children": {
                            "59": {
                              "id": "59",
                              "speaker": "Narrator",
                              "text": "*Whyever not? After all, you are an illithid - whatever flaws plagued you as a human are long behind you now.*",
                              "context": "CinematicNodeContext: Gale in Illithid form, flexing his Illithid magic, interwoven with Karsite magic\rInternalNodeContext: ILLITHID",
                              "checkflags": [
                                "FULL_CEREMORPH"
                              ],
                              "setflags": [],
                              "ruletags": [],
                              "approval": [],
                              "rolls": "",
                              "goto": "",
                              "link": "14",
                              "is_end": false,
                              "node_type": "normal",
                              "children": {}
                            },
                            "29": {
                              "id": "29",
                              "speaker": "Narrator",
                              "text": "*There's only one way to find out.*",
                              "context": "CinematicNodeContext: Gale, determined, the course is set",
                              "checkflags": [],
                              "setflags": [],
                              "ruletags": [],
                              "approval": [],
                              "rolls": "",
                              "goto": "",
                              "link": "",
                              "is_end": false,
                              "node_type": "normal",
                              "children": {
                                "14": {
                                  "id": "14",
                                  "speaker": "Narrator",
                                  "text": "*Within you, the orb strains against its confines. You sense Elminster's enchantment is beginning to fade. It will not be contained much longer, but that doesn't matter now.*",
                                  "context": "",
                                  "checkflags": [],
                                  "setflags": [],
                                  "ruletags": [],
                                  "approval": [],
                                  "rolls": "",
                                  "goto": "",
                                  "link": "",
                                  "is_end": false,
                                  "node_type": "normal",
                                  "children": {
                                    "42": {
                                      "id": "42",
                                      "speaker": "Narrator",
                                      "text": "*At last, the future unfolds before you. The power of Karsus in your hands. And no one, not the orb, not even the goddess of magic herself, is going to stop you.*",
                                      "context": "NodeContext: The orb is most definitely going to stop you, so maybe a hint of irony to the player's confidence here",
                                      "checkflags": [],
                                      "setflags": [],
                                      "ruletags": [],
                                      "approval": [],
                                      "rolls": "",
                                      "goto": "",
                                      "link": "",
                                      "is_end": true,
                                      "node_type": "normal",
                                      "children": {}
                                    }
                                  }
                                }
                              }
                            }
                          }
                        }
                      }
                    },
                    "15": {
                      "id": "15",
                      "speaker": "Player",
                      "text": "Reforge the Crown. Offer it to Mystra, hope that it's enough for her to cure you of the orb.",
                      "context": "",
                      "checkflags": [
                        "ORI_Gale_Knows_ReadKarsusNotes"
                      ],
                      "setflags": [
                        "ORI_Gale_Event_GaveCrownToMystra"
                      ],
                      "ruletags": [],
                      "approval": [],
                      "rolls": "",
                      "goto": "",
                      "link": "",
                      "is_end": false,
                      "node_type": "normal",
                      "children": {
                        "24": {
                          "id": "24",
                          "speaker": "Narrator",
                          "text": "*Hope. For so long you scarcely dared to think the word, never mind feel it. But you dare to feel it now. How could you not. You are loved. And you are at peace.*",
                          "context": "",
                          "checkflags": [
                            "ORI_State_Partnered"
                          ],
                          "setflags": [],
                          "ruletags": [],
                          "approval": [],
                          "rolls": "",
                          "goto": "",
                          "link": "",
                          "is_end": false,
                          "node_type": "normal",
                          "children": {
                            "33": {
                              "id": "33",
                              "speaker": "",
                              "text": "",
                              "context": "",
                              "checkflags": [],
