        "8": {
          "id": "8",
          "speaker": "Narrator",
          "text": "*You felt the magic of Karsus draining from the stones as the Crown plummeted to the bottom of the Chionthar. A useless trinket, nothing more.*",
          "context": "",
          "checkflags": [
            "REALLY_GALE"
          ],
          "setflags": [],
          "ruletags": [],
          "approval": [],
          "rolls": "",
          "goto": "",
          "link": "36",
          "is_end": false,
          "node_type": "normal",
          "children": {
            "45": {
              "id": "45",
              "speaker": "Narrator",
              "text": "*At least the mortal world will be safe from the temptation of the Crown. But you...*",
              "context": "",
              "checkflags": [],
              "setflags": [],
              "ruletags": [],
              "approval": [],
              "rolls": "",
              "goto": "",
              "link": "36",
              "is_end": false,
              "node_type": "normal",
              "children": {
                "10": {
                  "id": "10",
                  "speaker": "Narrator",
                  "text": "*You are an illithid, your body ravaged by ceremorphosis, your mind prey to unfamiliar desires to consume, to devour.*",
                  "context": "",
                  "checkflags": [
                    "FULL_CEREMORPH"
                  ],
                  "setflags": [],
                  "ruletags": [],
                  "approval": [],
                  "rolls": "",
                  "goto": "",
                  "link": "36",
                  "is_end": false,
                  "node_type": "normal",
                  "children": {
                    "18": {
                      "id": "18",
                      "speaker": "Narrator",
                      "text": "*And what of the orb? Already you sense Elminster's enchantment fading. Will you still be able to prevent its explosion when you can barely control yourself?*",
                      "context": "",
                      "checkflags": [],
                      "setflags": [],
                      "ruletags": [],
                      "approval": [],
                      "rolls": "",
                      "goto": "",
                      "link": "",
                      "is_end": false,
                      "node_type": "normal",
                      "children": {
                        "28": {
                          "id": "28",
                          "speaker": "Player",
                          "text": "You will claim the Crown of Karsus. It is your right. Your destiny.",
                          "context": "",
                          "checkflags": [
                            "ORI_Gale_Knows_ReadKarsusNotes = False"
                          ],
                          "setflags": [
                            "ORI_Gale_State_ClaimedCrown"
